data.description: Close to town with a country feel!  Take a look at this beautiful and spacious 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home.  With a sprawling layout, there is plenty of room for everyone!  The main floor boasts an entry way with tall ceilings and a winding staircase.  The oversized living room has a stone gas fireplace, huge windows, and vaulted ceilings letting in tons of natural light.  Opening to the dining room.  Gorgeous kitchen with custom cabinets and granite and second dining area.  Plenty of workspace. Main floor primary bedroom with a full bath and walk in closet.  Attached is the main floor laundry.  The upstairs has 2 large bedrooms that share full bath and both have walk in closets.  Downstairs the massive basement has tons of room for entertaining, another bedroom, and tons of storage.  Enjoy the 1/2 acre lot with mature trees while you enjoy sitting out on the deck that spans the side and back of the home.  Home Warranty Provided!   Schedule your showing today!!!
